      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Opmerkingen van Mark over problemen met ontwikkeling: <a style="color:#69aa35;" href="evernote:///view/2147483647/s213/c177f3be-ad93-4dd1-bfae-394b54f7bf8a/c177f3be-ad93-4dd1-bfae-394b54f7bf8a/">NS OBIS 2017</a></div><div><br/></div><div> </div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
