<div style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 36pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; text-indent: -18pt;"><span style="font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">         </span></span><span style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125);"><a shape="rect" href="http://lodar.de/" style="color: purple; text-decoration: underline;">Lodar.de</a></span></div>
